 </div>	<div class="pub-bg">
		<div class="container news-details">
					<h1 class=" te_c">西藏民族大学附属医院视频监控系统二级等保测评服务竞争性谈判公告</h1>
					<div class="info te_c">
						<span>发布时间：2026-06-15</span>
						<span>浏览次数：<pageview id="fd89cd29-e2e9-4060-9562-c77b18ace4ba" >0</pageview><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){$.ajax({url: "/Server/Preview/callBack/News/PageView",type: "POST",data: {newsId:"fd89cd29-e2e9-4060-9562-c77b18ace4ba"},success: function(result) {if (result.success){$("#fd89cd29-e2e9-4060-9562-c77b18ace4ba").text(result.data.pageView);}}});});</script></span>
					</div>
					<div class="line p_r"></div>
					<div class="body">
						<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">根据工作需要，我院需对</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">“视频监控系统二级等保测评服务”进行采购，该项目将以竞争性谈判的方式进行，欢迎符合资质条件的供应商前来响应及报价。</span></span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">一、项目概况</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">1.项目</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">名称</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">：西藏民族大学附属医院视频监控系统二级等保测评服务采购项目</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">2.服务内容：视频监控系统二级等保测评服务</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">3.服务期限：一年（自合同签订之日起）</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">4.项目预算：40000元</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">5.</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">成交数量：开标时不少于</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">3家单位方可开标</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">，</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">确定</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">1家</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">。</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">二、报名需提供以下资质或证明</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">1.参加采购活动前三年内，在经营活动中没有重大违法记录；</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">2.单位负责人为同一人或者存在控股、管理关系的不同单位，不得参加同一项目采购；</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;" align="justify"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">3.投标人不得为“中国执行信息公开网（zxgk.court.gov.cn）”被列入失信被执行人名单；“信用中国（ww.creditchina.gov.cn）”重大税收违法失信主体名单（以截图打印并加盖单位鲜章为准）；</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">4.提供中国合格评定国家认可委员会检验机构认可证书CNAS以及检验监测机构资质认定证书CMA证书；</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">5.项目投入高级测评师不得少于2人，中级测评师不得少于4人，初级测评师不得少于3人；</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">6.应提供至少一年的信息安全应急处理保障服务；</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">7.本次采购不接受联合体投标。</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">三、报名时间</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">202</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">6</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">年</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">6</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">月</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">15</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">日起至</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">202</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">6</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">年</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">6</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">月</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">18</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">日（节假日和非工作时间除外），上午</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;">9:00-11:30；14:30-17:00。</span></span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">四、报名地点</span></p> 
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 32.0000pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000; line-height: 28.0000pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 等线; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">网上报名邮箱号：</span><a href="mailto:1300465956@qq.com"><u><span class="15" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #0563c1; font-size: 16pt;">1300465956@qq.com</span></u></a></p> 
